1964;;Ring of Spies;;British;;Robert Tronson;;Bernard Lee, William Sylvester;;spy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ring_of_Spies;;A dissatisfied Navy clerk begins handling secret documents when he is approached by secret Soviet intelligence to hand over documents to them. Although he is being blackmailed, he agrees to do so while also being paid for the information. He begins an affair with the secretary who also has access to greater secret documents. Together, the couple continue to procure information for Soviet intelligence while getting paid. Soon, the British government gets wind of their betrayal.